Colour . Live specimens with light brown carapace, darker brown on anterior part. Chelipeds, walking legs, and abdomen are lighter than carapace, sometimes with brown banding on the walking legs. Dark brown setae are on the outer surface of the manus of the chelipeds and on upper margin of propodus of the walking legs, giving a darker appearance to these parts (
Naderloo & Türkay 2009
).
